  return <View><Animated.View style={style}><Pressable accessibilityRole="button" accessibilityLabel="Page header that crossfades on tab change" accessibilityHint="Activates without requiring motion or gestures" accessibilityActions={[{name:'activate',label:'Activate'}]} onAccessibilityAction={activate} hitSlop={{top:8,right:8,bottom:8,left:8}} style={{minHeight:44,minWidth:44}} onPressIn={() => { progress.value = withTiming(1, {duration: reduceMotion ? 0 : 120}); }} onPressOut={() => { progress.value = withTiming(0, {duration: reduceMotion ? 0 : 160}); }} onPress={activate}><Text>Page header that crossfades on tab change</Text></Pressable></Animated.View></View>;
}

